"al-Transfir" al-Isra'iliyah fi al-tatbiq, 1949-1996 / 
Nur al-Din Masalhah. al-Tab'ah 1. Bayrut : Mu'assasat 
al-Dirasat al-Filastiniyah, 1997. $8.20 (U.S.). xii, 
